title: My pixel 4a 5g will not power on after a restart. Battery charged to approx 90%. Tried common tips
content: I did a restart after I tried to delete an email and the program stopped. I touched the power button to restart and the screen went dark like always but now it's not turning back on. I've tried all the common tips from the trouble shooting suggestions. Any other help ? Please help. I've only had the phone since March 2021
